1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema toga.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osobito je pitanje za nas koji živimo ovdje iz kršćanske tradicije.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pitanje je tko je to svet?

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Obično mislimo da su sveci neki strani ljudi.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neki čudni ljudi.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neki koji žive u kutu života.

7
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Drugi mislite da su sveci neki pobožni ljudi.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda imate ti koji idu u crku pa obaraju pogled, pa lijepo isklope ruke, pa krunica sve tamo do koljena velika.

9
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je izgledati pobožan, to nema ništa sa svetošću.

10
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda obično mislimo da ljudi koji su dobri, da su oni sveti.

11
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate koliko imate dobrih ljudi oko nas.

12
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeliko proglašen svetim što je dobar.

13
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda mislimo da su sveti ljudi kad recimo kad oni meditiraju po cijele dane, pa trasadentalnu meditaciju, pa onda koje kakve druge, hinduističke, budističke, šintoističke, reikiske i tako dalje.

14
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, još nikoga meditacija je napravila boljim čovjekom.

15
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

16
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svece najmanje.

17
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može.

18
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome, dakle, je uvijek pitanje, a ko je to onda svetac?

19
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto su Ivanu Pavlu drugom, odmah kad je umirao još ti nije umrao i vikali santo, santo, svetac, zašto?

20
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] U čemu je on bio drugačiji od drugih ljudi?

21
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto nismo kad je pio 12. umirali, rekli santo, santo?

22
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

23
00:01:55,000 --> 00:02:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je papa pao 6. umirao, prije ovoga, Ivana Pavla druga, zašto nismo uvikali santo? Ne, ništa.

24
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] A isto je papa.

25
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Molio.

26
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja zdavno radi u Vatikanu sam radio, on je plakao često puta pred oltarom.

27
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad su toliko napadali posto koncila i teolozi i drugi i crkvu i njega i tako dalje.

28
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Boko poboža nam ništa.

29
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je to svetost?

30
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što to ima Ivan Pavla druga, mi ne.

31
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je to mala Terezija imala, mi ne.

32
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je to imao Ivan Merc, a ti i ja?

33
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma bit ćeo mi bolje od njega.

34
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači da se ne isplati živjeta ako nećemo.

35
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost. Što je to dakle svetost?

36
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svatite.

37
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kažemo da je samo Bog svet,

38
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] pokušajte misliti, šta vi po ti mislite?

39
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zar ne, obično zamišljamo

40
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] da svet zato što njiva niko ne može dodirati.

41
00:02:56,000 --> 00:03:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je u nedostupnom svijetlu, kaže Ivan u svojom evanđelju.

42
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako u nedostupnom svijetlu, a ja dostupno?

43
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus meni dostupan, uzmem hosti u Isusu.

44
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Boga vidim na svakom koraku, kako nedostupan?

45
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što mi nije to Bože svetost.

46
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kažemo svijetlu, mislimo, o onda je to Bog savršen, dobar, ovo ono.

47
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ljudi toliko optužuju Boga da on krivi, što djeca umiru, što nevi ni sredavi, što ovo što ono, eto ti bo krivi na svakom koraku.

48
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači nije ni to. Što je tu zapravo svetost? Šta mislimo po tim kad kažemo svetost?

49
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svatit ćete ako je dobro razumijete.

50
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je svet, a to znači, samo on ima snagu protiv zla.

51
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ta snaga tom je kao kad upalite svjetlo i mrak bježi.

52
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost je kad dođete iz tame pa u svjetlo.

53
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost je nešto što kao peč kad joj zagrijete u hladnoj sobi, a ona zrači, a tebi milina bi tu i još to je dobro.

54
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sino se vraćamo negdje prije ponoći.

55
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ta ona kaptorina sa peče, sliše smo onima koji štrajkuju glađu, pa s nima morali krunicu, pa se vraćamo, a zima smrznuli smo se.

56
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I uđemo u tom samo u hodnika, kaže jedna od studionice, kaže: "I još to ovdje toplo. Što je to toplo?"

57
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećam se kad sam bio sa Ivanom Pavlom drugim, razgovarali smo, dakle, kad sam imao prvi puta duhovnu lježba njegovim gardistima, onda mi je komandant natjerao da moram ići u audijenciju k njemu.

58
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najprije nisam pio, sam uvijek mislio, a bio sam na stotinu audijencija kod Ivana Pavla, kod Pavla šesto, kod ovog, kod onog.

59
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pape, ajde moj, nema tu njihova. Kao kod druge.

60
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao sam da ne.

61
00:04:54,000 --> 00:05:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda me on ipak uvijeruje da bi bilo dobro, da sam trebao petak putovati, a u suboto sam mogo ići u audijenciju, jer papa je bio isto duhovnim vježbama, kada i njegovji gardisti.

62
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kada mi kaže da suboto je moj, haj, imam kartu za petak. I on meni promijeni kartu, šta sve ni napravio jedan tam čovjek.

63
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u suboto je zaista se sastane s papom, koji je bio mi prvi dojam? Jednostavan.

64
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] On vam je mogo ispričati ako treba sto vijceva.

65
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] O sve ono se kratko na onaj svoj štab.

66
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] I s ovo je gleda u oči. I smiješi se. I kaže: "A tako, a vi ste moj, ti ste moj, duhovni."

67
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem ja da: "Jo, hvala vam, sad ću imati bolje ljude, sad ću imati sigurnije."

68
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I smiješim i se i gledam. Jednostavno čovjek, najjednostavniji čovjek.

69
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] I šta posebno u njemu.

70
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali pokraj toga svega nam izračio nešto sasvim drugo.

71
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao kad peć grije. Kao kad te svijetlo basija.

72
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao kad djete uđe u onaj okvir majčini drugoli.

73
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Majka je tu dobra, prestaje plakati.

74
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto što zračio, nešto toplo, nešto životo.

75
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kao ono što kažemo život iz tebe zračio.

76
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto neizrecivo.

77
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] I smo razgovarali 5 do 10 minuta.

78
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šalili se svakako. Pa jeste vi kaže njima govorili Hrvatske.

79
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nekako ću Hrvatska uniši carci.

80
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao bi razumijeli. Pa dobro kažem.

81
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njemački sam govorio.

82
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, ma nemojte. Pa jeste. Pa šta ste vi to kaže govorili?

83
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nekako ono što vi obično govorili.

84
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma šta to kaže, ne bi me li recite.

85
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono ja njemu odužao mali seminar.

86
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] O egzistenciji.

87
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, o, o, o.

88
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Papa sluša sam stojeno.

89
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako dalje, i tako dalje.

90
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se završila ta audijencija, ja nisam mogao vjerovat.

91
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko put sam bio u razima audijencijama drugih papa.

92
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je tu bilo? To me je tako duboko dinulo.

93
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja do danas to ne mogu zaboraviti.

94
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto drugo u mene ušlo.

95
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ne ušlo, ne.

96
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto što stalno grije.

97
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako toplo.

98
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam sad joj, to je svetost.

99
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad sam se pitao, pa kako to človjek postaje sveto?

100
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sjetim kad je papa tek postao papa, on je meni tako frajerski izgledao.

101
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao ja u mlađim godinama.

102
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je tako znao se pravi dvaža, on je bio športaš, on je bio glumac.

103
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je znao, znate, prvi njegov nastup je bio onaj:

104
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ja sam to."

105
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je nastupio.

106
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Baš kao Isus ono nakon uskrsnuća.

107
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ti je reći to, pa ne bojte se ako sam ja Poljak.

108
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo izabrali Italijana opet, jeli.

109
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] 450 godina u Italijani bili papa.

110
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bojte se, ja sam to.

111
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko humora je uvijek bilo u njemu i da je to strašio.

112
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sjeća se dakle taj športski tip.

113
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] To on se pravio da opravi dvaža.

114
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je nam popravo posvijek smijao.

115
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nasmije se, naprave ovo i onu primedu i tako dalje.

116
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što se nije napravio.

117
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad je pomalo počela reuma u njemu i ne znam boliti ga noga,

118
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda je naredio kardinalova da mu naprave, da mu iskopaju bazen.

119
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi on plivao.

120
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Su rekli: "Sve ti oče pravi ćemo trošiti novce još na te gluposti."

121
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] A on ima kaže: "Dobro.

122
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ćete trošiti novce na moj pokop i biranju novog pape.

123
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da vidimo što vam je bolje.

124
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta vas manje košta."

125
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] I morali smo iskopati.

126
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I plivao je.

127
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost je zapravo, vidite, nešto gdje Bog zapravo u nekome bude.

128
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nije u tom smislu kako mi to bude.

129
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo kao ono kad je u trudnici dijete pa na dijete djači.

130
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

131
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trudnica nije zato fascinantna što je dijete u njoj, nego što je trudnica.

132
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je to Božje čedo, Božje stvorede u njoj.

133
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je blagoslovljena.

134
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je ništo drugo.

135
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nije u njoj.

136
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog Boga koji joj je darao djete i blagoslovljena tu divnu ženu.

137
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najljepša u vide trudnice kad idu preko cijete.

138
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj, milina mi.

139
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma bih stavio auto i vozio cijeli dan.

140
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zbogoslovljena je žena.

141
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dugo sam ih smetivao kak se to postaje svet.

142
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam mislio da treba puno moliti.

143
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam molio i satima i satima.

144
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dok sam skoro slomio koljeno od klečanja.

145
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda sam mislio da postite.

146
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam znao da postite kako.

147
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam vidio da izgladnio sam.

148
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mršar sam bio u kosti i koža.

149
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nigde svetosti.

150
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda sam izučio meditaciju.

151
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam napisao čak svoju prvu knjigu oče.

152
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I unutra točno razradio kako se meditira.

153
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam meditirao, pa meditirao.

154
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam razlomio noge, ali ništa od svega.

155
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Od sve te meditacije.

156
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa ja nisam bio bolji človjek.

157
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možda sam bio nešto malo bolji.

158
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to nije to.

159
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije svetost.

160
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost je ono kad imate došle.

161
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj smijem li te samo dodinuti.

162
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] U tebi je nešto drugo.

163
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se sjeti majke Tereze.

164
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bila je u Frankopanskoj stanovala.

165
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono kad je dolazila u Hrvatsku.

166
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam išao sa Don Lukom de Polom.

167
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da joj posjetim.

168
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da razgovaramo malo.

169
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kad joj vidiš.

170
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sirota onako pogrebljena sva.

171
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sa borama na licu.

172
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što bih rekao nema ženstvenosti.

173
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma kak je vrhunska ženstvenost.

174
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da bila kod frizera tamo je bila neženstvena.

175
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sa podelanim papućama.

176
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sa ovo sa ovo.

177
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] A milina sam još potreba.

178
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo da odinem ruku.

179
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje je nebo.

180
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je ništa sasvim drugo.

181
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sam razmišljao kako i kako.

182
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda tok nisam jednog dana odlučio da ću ja.

183
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tri tjedna.

184
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan po 20 minuta.

185
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sprećat pred Bogom.

186
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno gledat u njega.

187
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I očekivati njegovu pomog.

188
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Priznavat svoje grije sam i tako.

189
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali očekivati.

190
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost je nešto što dolazi od Boga.

191
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] To Bog dan.

192
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti možeš postati.

193
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam kako dobar.

194
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš dijeliti milosti.

195
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš razdijeliti sve.

196
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svet Pao kaže.

197
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to ljubav.

198
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] A Bog je ljubav.

199
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš postati.

200
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,000
[UNKNOWN] Moliti.

201
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš se trapiti.

202
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš sve.

203
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,000
[UNKNOWN] Ne.

204
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije svetost.

205
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Opet si onaj jednostavno čovjek koji nema niš u sebi.

206
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko kamen.

207
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne zračiš.

208
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo Bog može se ne zračiti.

209
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kad sam navučio i shvatio kada je Papa postao svet.

210
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam ga gledao toliko puta.

211
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo razgovarajući s time.

212
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo čitajući o njemu i druge.

213
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Slušajući druge.

214
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] On vam ode u kapelicu i on pol sata sat.

215
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] On samo uroni.

216
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uronio Isuse Hrista.

217
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] On kad moli krunicu onda ne moli:

218
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Zdravo molimo isti punog zmojeg vas djevica"

219
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

220
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Zdravo Marija"

221
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ave Marija"

222
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imaš oseća a on ju vidi.

223
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] On se ti vam razgovara.

224
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kada on govori o Isusu.

225
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je to Isus.

226
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ga vidim.

227
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ga susrećem.

228
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz njega i u njem.

229
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je čudesno nešto.

230
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dakle kad sam nakon ta tri tjedna doživio to prvi susret to je već bilo nešto.

231
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali šta je ta bio susret?

232
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije kao da ja sam tri tjedna moli obo se ja nešto postigao.

233
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] O ne.

234
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliki ljudi su probali na isti način.

235
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekli su: "Vi ste tri tjedna i sad ću ja probati tri tjedna."

236
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Baš je onaj komandant.

237
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Papini gardista mi je reo kad smo se vraćali sa audijencije od pape.

238
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda meni kaže:

239
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] "I ja sam odlučio da ću ja tako tri tjedna."

240
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja rekao: "Ne znam ba ga li ćeš uskjeti."

241
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nije stvar o tome da klečiš i da te 20 minuta svaki dan ne ga.

242
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je klik?

243
00:12:56,000 --> 00:13:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad sam shvatio što je toliko primjera drugih.

244
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio mi je fascinantan onaj primjer.

245
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje njegov propovjednik korizmeni kantala mesa.

246
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad dolazio upravo a ja sam zapao u onaj teški promet rimski.

247
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije se mogao izvući.

248
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zakastio pol sata.

249
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kardinali čekaju.

250
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Cijela vatikanska kurija.

251
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi ovi patini službenici njih.

252
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tko zna koliko sto, 200, 300.

253
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaju.

254
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kardinali bijesni.

255
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je?

256
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne papa, ću vidjeti da njega nema.

257
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ošao on u kapelicu.

258
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je došao kantala mesa ispričava se ovi ljuti svi kardinali.

259
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] A papa mirno opušten došao.

260
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je?

261
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je ošao u kapelicu.

262
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] i fino uronio Isusa Hrista i njegovu prisutnost.

263
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] I došao tu i slušao.

264
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo on.

265
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam shvatio dakle da zapravo svetost uopće nije u moralnosti tvojoj.

266
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ni u pobožnosti tvojoj.

267
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ni u tome da se praviš pobožan.

268
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ni u tome da puno klećiš.

269
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ni da puno posliš.

270
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da je pobožnost samo u tome da li otvoraš vrata Kristu.

271
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kristu.

272
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] To što je ovaj papa znao govoriti otvorite Kristu vrata.

273
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je sve.

274
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kada ja dođem u kapelicu pa kleknem.

275
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda meni prvo to.

276
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa tu si.

277
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja drago mi je.

278
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što dođe k meni.

279
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda samo svjestan ostanem.

280
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] bar pol minute.

281
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Minutu.

282
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dvije.

283
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda osjeti.

284
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Živje.

285
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu smo.

286
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad možemo razgovarati.

287
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] To znači.

288
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] To se samo da pričekaš.

289
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svijestam.

290
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem.

291
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si tu.

292
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tada ja ostavno tvoj duh polako.

293
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko oživi.

294
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Duh Boži te nadahne.

295
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti vidiš njega i ti s njim razgovaraš.

296
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I smiješ se.

297
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] I da ostavno.

298
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] 5-6 minuta.

299
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam što treba vama govoriti.

300
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] I na taj način.

301
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle.

302
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam to naučio polako.

303
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidio sam.

304
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je taj Papa Ivan Pavel drugi.

305
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je fasciniralo.

306
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kod mladih i drugih.

307
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa on se znao šalit nas to načina.

308
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je najzgodnije bilo kad je bio.

309
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad on ovaj.

310
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mladji mu svira i on vrti svoj štap.

311
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda mu njegovu tajni kaže.

312
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ti oče.

313
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste pije papa.

314
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nemući tako se igrati.

315
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vrti svojim štapom.

316
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da plešiš.

317
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili u Parisu tamo nam on martruje.

318
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sa mladima susret.

319
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne.

320
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda on već 23 sata je.

321
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on mladima.

322
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Drogi i mladi.

323
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja moram ići na spavanje.

324
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vam spavam.

325
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uvidom samostarno.

326
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Učasnim se stara.

327
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono je sigurno već legle.

328
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neće mi otvoriti.

329
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad će vani cijelu noć.

330
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prepun humora i jednostavnost.

331
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Taj cijelu je uspio to kapirati.

332
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve to je samo u tome.

333
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] To pustiš svetom da bude u tebi.

334
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad je Bog u tebi.

335
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] To ti postaješ drugačiji.

336
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tada je to snaga njegova koja tebe mijenja.

337
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda zrači na druge ljude oko tebe i druge mijenja.

338
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sto puta sam razočarao kad sam mislio.

339
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da kad ja držim seminare.

340
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da to zapravo moje pametne riječi.

341
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Misli.

342
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam si to sastavio.

343
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najprej egzistencijalno predavanje.

344
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda obrađenje.

345
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa o molitvi.

346
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa o grijehu.

347
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa o ovo.

348
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa o crkvi.

349
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sve.

350
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da to ljudima.

351
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad sam ja uvidio.

352
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da svi moji govorema baš ne postižu ništa ko ljudima dosađuju.

353
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da sam bio razočaran.

354
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] I pitao sam se što to namijenja.

355
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi sam zapazio.

356
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja prije seminara dva dana.

357
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pod sad, dva, tri.

358
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] S pred njega samo stojim i slušam.

359
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Slušam.

360
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne govori Bogu.

361
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uništit ćete molitva koju govoriš.

362
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Promijenit ćete molitva u kojoj slušaš Boga.

363
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer molitva je razgovor s Bogom.

364
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo zvoni, dugo čekaj.

365
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Izgovori te koju rečenici jeste tu sam.

366
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I čekaj.

367
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] O slušku.

368
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ono te mijenja što Bog kaže.

369
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono će te izlječiti što Isus tebi rekla.

370
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] A nemo što ti njemu govoriš.

371
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I najljepše molite će te uništiti jer šta one zamijene.

372
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti stalno sad ću Hildegardinu.

373
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] A sad ću od Svetog Ignacija.

374
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] A sad ću ovu.

375
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] A sad ću Krunci.

376
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus kaže pusti ga.

377
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ido mi doma.

378
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono nema vreme na tebi ništa dati jer ti mu ne došli do riječi.

379
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jel je to bezobrazilo.

380
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećam se jedne gospođe.

381
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njega je jedna gospođa mi nazivala uvijek.

382
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Radihagiju terapije.

383
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jel je na telefon.

384
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda na ovu kuhinju obječno kuha.

385
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda šta.

386
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ta gospođa kad nas zove.

387
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se toliko priča da ova ne mre doći do riječi.

388
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I šta ona napravlja.

389
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, dobro, dobro.

390
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] I stavi lijepo telefon tamo.

391
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] I pol sata ona je bezbrga.

392
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ona se radi okolo što god hoće.

393
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ova priča.

394
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle nakraj dođe.

395
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Je li bilo doviđenja?

396
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije ona još priča.

397
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su naše molice.

398
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sam shvatio da otvorenost duše.

399
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da Bog smije k' meni doći.

400
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to povjerenje da on tu da ga nakon.

401
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] I da je on ovdje.

402
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] I da moj duh je sposoban njega primiti.

403
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer moj duh isto je bezgraničan.

404
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje od Boga meni darovan.

405
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pravno taj duh može primiti sve moguće.

406
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad to sastane se susret.

407
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je to.

408
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko puta sam znao se čuti.

409
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mi ljudi dođu na mojim seminjarnom.

410
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže jel smiju vas samo dirnut u rame.

411
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao šta jeste zaljubljen u meli?

412
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ne kaže.

413
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] U vama je Isus.

414
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako?

415
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Za mi u vama.

416
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj iz vas zrači.

417
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gleda me.

418
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Grozno.

419
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] A vijek sam mislil da to ja nešto napravim.

420
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da sam to ja zgodan, inteligentan sposoban.

421
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Napravim vid sebe.

422
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vas nasmijem da kažem joj idemo i Ivanšću.

423
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma šta.

424
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad mi ljudi kaže.

425
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] A kad vi govorite.

426
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nešto izlazi.

427
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] To zrači.

428
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije riječ.

429
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije riječ.

430
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije govori.

431
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,000
[UNKNOWN] I to je to.

432
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ako ja k vama dođem.

433
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam pa pol sata bio pred njim.

434
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao gospodine moj.

435
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti ćeš govoriti.

436
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću tebi sam biti mikrofon.

437
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ti govoriš.

438
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to ne napravim.

439
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je uzelo.

440
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ako vam pitate šta je svetost.

441
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle šta je svetost.

442
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo to.

443
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost je u tome da drugi ljudi zapažaju.

444
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] To bi nešto drugo.

445
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] I žele s tobom biti.

446
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da sam tako dobro govorio.

447
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Seda od 4-5 godina sam učio u Frankopansko sa studentima.

448
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vrhunski vjeronauku.

449
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vrhunske propojde.

450
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vrhunske misle.

451
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pjevanje.

452
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve smo uredili da mi lina.

453
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] A neko nije ostale.

454
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onako sve dobro.

455
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo smo sa idemo dalje.

456
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja razočaram.

457
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Te kad sam ja ovako temeljito išao do Boga.

458
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] I njega udahnuo.

459
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako sam osjetio kako svi.

460
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tad niče niko ni odlazio.

461
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi su dolazili.

462
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi su i htjeli biti samom.

463
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prije sam ja uvijek tražio da mi neko dođe.

464
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne budem sam.

465
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osobito nedeljom posle povodne.

466
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo će me ubići čoveče.

467
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Niko ne treba Ivančića.

468
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam ja ovo doživio.

469
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sada sam moram zaključavati vrata.

470
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vadi telefonici.

471
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako su bili oni.

472
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zida.

473
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dojade.

474
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da mi liče.

475
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mira.

476
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi moća biti samom.

477
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo gdje je Bog.

478
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo je fascinacija.

479
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo je sve.

480
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo je ljubo.

481
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sveta si niko drugi niko koji dopušta da Bog kroz njega gleda ljude.

482
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govori ljudima.

483
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Djeluje.

484
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] I uvijek sam se pitao.

485
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa čemu je sveti Petar bio svet?

486
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je on svet?

487
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Petrova svet.

488
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma niti on bio bolji.

489
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ba kako je ni milimetar.

490
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ni pod noktam nije bio postao bolji.

491
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus mu rekao jedan puta odlazi s Sotanom.

492
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nigdje ne piše da je on postao bolji čovje.

493
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pavel.

494
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma prije se svađao i nakreo je svađao.

495
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Posadio se sa Jadimonim Barnabom da je bilo strašno.

496
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na mačeve tako reći.

497
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi što nikad nisu gledali.

498
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dok mi je došao do haggioterapije pa se obraćao.

499
00:20:55,000 --> 00:21:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Niko od njih nije postao ni za prst bolji.

500
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toma.

501
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] No, slobodi Bože.

502
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko.

503
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni se pitao po čemu su oni sveti?

504
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo zato.

505
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što su na duhove tako duboko osjetili kako je ušao Isusa u duhu u njih.

506
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad Isus rađi.

507
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su za njega išli umrije.

508
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni govore lijepo o vanjom djelu.

509
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govore velikim svećnicima.

510
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Više treba slušati Boga neko vas ljude.

511
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi su njega doživjeli.

512
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je u njima i mi ne možemo drugačije.

513
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možemo ne biti ono što jesmo.

514
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zato govorimo to što on nama daje.

515
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo po tome što su oni voljeli Isusa.

516
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što su vjerovali njemu.

517
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što su mu bili prijatelji u tome svetosti.

518
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] U ličem drugom.

519
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ako vam pitate što će promijeniti Hrvatsko i svijet i Evropu.

520
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo oni ljudi koji budu imali hrabrosti to u sebe upiti.

521
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ivana papa druga u cijeli svijet je slušao.

522
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I političari i ateisti ima sve.

523
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kako on srušio komunizam i berlinski zid.

524
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mi je pričao teolog iz Meksika kako su oni imali sto godina komunizam kod njih gori nego kod nas.

525
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je papa došao prvi put da kaže u Meksiko i predsjednik Republike nije smio ga primiti.

526
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ustavu ne smije primiti papu.

527
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni su bili protivi crka.

528
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Crka bila progojena užasno kod njih.

529
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je samo privatno došao kaže evo ja ne smijem drugačije ja vas pozdravljam kaže evo prepuštam vas narodu.

530
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] I je papa došao na ko godinu opet drugi puta pa treći pa četvrti puta pala komunistička vlast.

531
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je demokratska vlast kod njih.

532
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa pozor nije radio.

533
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubio te ljude niš drugo.

534
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] I one koji su neprijatelji.

535
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je sepac.

536
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ste vidjeli kad je bio bolisan?

537
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ništa.

538
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže mu njemački teoloz i papa pa ne možeš takav biti na televiziji sramota te gledati.

539
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gle kako si.

540
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Parkinson je iz obličeno lice.

541
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam Isusu rekao do kraja života.

542
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad mu došao Ratzinger, umrla mu sestra pa je bio strašno tužan sadašnji dakle papa.

543
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] A bio je pročelnik Kongregacije za nauke vjere pa mu kaže sveti oče.

544
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dajte zamijenite mi nek pa drugi ne mogu više.

545
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imam sedmdeset i korko.

546
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šest godina.

547
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] A sa sedmdeset pet imam pravo otiće.

548
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže mu ovaj pa o drugim.

549
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne Jozefe.

550
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ostaćaš dok li ja.

551
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti su zapravo ljudi kroz čije oči vi vidite Boga.

552
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz čije tijelo vi ga zapravo pipate, doživljavate.

553
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz čije život ponaša vi osjećate među nama živi Boga.

554
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Eto to.

555
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to su ljudi zbog kojim je osjećat da ima lijepo bit na zemlji.

556
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] A to je kako sad tužno.

557
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema majke Tereze.

558
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema Ivana Pavla drugom.

559
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trebamo ponovno svećati.

560
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi to zovemo trebamo vođu.

561
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan Pavla drugi bio vođa.

562
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što je bio svećan.

563
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer samo Isus vođa.

564
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže nikoga ne zovite vođom.

565
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan je vaš vođa.

566
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus Kristus.

567
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

568
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome tko upije Isusa Kristus.

569
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je vođa?

570
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi predsjednik tužan bio vjeliki vođa Hrvatske.

571
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da li on sam iz komunizma svoga prešao i postao kršćan.

572
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što sve nije radio.

573
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ispovjedao se išao u crkvi.

574
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Priznavao to.

575
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi moglo biti.

576
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vođa koja vode prema dobru.

577
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moje mora biti ispunjeni Boga.

578
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle ako ste me shvatili što god bit će dobro.

579
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako niste, a šta ću s vama?

580
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću opet sljedeći puta.

581
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vam je strašno važno znati svetost.

582
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo sveti ljudi će promijeniti Hrvatsku i ove nove izbore.

583
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da dođu sveti ljudi na vlast.

584
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] A onda će nam biti dobro.

585
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] A svetac nije dobar čovjek.

586
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

587
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Iskaže nikog ne zovite dobro.

588
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

589
00:25:08,000 --> 00:25:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema dobrih ljudi.

590
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi griježi.

591
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetac nije pobožnjak.

592
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osobodi Božem.

593
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi li župnici ne vole.

594
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo gnjave kaže.

595
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može da ključati crkvu od njih.

596
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo traže ispoved, ispoved, ispoved.

597
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oooo.

598
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Blagoslo, blagoslo, blagoslo.

599
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije to.

600
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je sve izvana.

601
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Izutra moraš primiti.

602
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ništa, nikakve meditacije, nikakve prakse.

603
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ćeš postati s Isusom prijatelj ili nećeš nikada ispuniti život.

604
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sa smisla.

605
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je Bog postao svoga sina, dakle stvoritelj svijeta.

606
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, idi reci, pokaži se živ kao što je.

607
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tu je rješenje.

608
00:25:55,000 --> 00:26:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi u meni, ja u vama, kažemo, savršeno jedno.

609
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ako mi ljubite, čuvat ćete moju riječ.

610
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] I k vama ću doći i kod vas se nastaniti.

611
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je sve to, ništa druga.

612
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako što vidite stvari koje gortujem.

613
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam imao jednu emisiju sada na novoj televiziji u nedjelju u jedan sat.

614
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekli su mi ovaj došli k meni i molim da ide, pa biću.

615
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže pol sata, kaže šte meni pol sata, a tamo se zatrčem u pol sata.

616
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam ovdje sat i pol, pa jedva izgovorim ono što mi treba.

617
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže, znate, televizija, televizija, to vam je pol sata, to je strašno puno, kaže.

618
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se umorimo pol sata, pa ako ja budem po cijeli sat, na televiziji pa mi ništa.

619
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo mi.

620
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi, ništa dobro, a nek bude pol sata.

621
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam samo da čujem, ljudi se samo se snebivaju.

622
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako dobro, kak se dobro izgledali, kak se to dobro izgledali, kak se svaki puta izgovarali, šta je to?

623
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ti se čudio, ja sam on rapoštovan.

624
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam sasvim normalno govorio.

625
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Obični Ivančić.

626
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prije toga sam naravno bio u kapelici dugo i dok su me vozili tamo na Novo, ja sam samo samo rekao isto, šefe, ti imaš biti u prvom planu.

627
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti imaš biti u prvom planu, ti imaš govoriti.

628
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer tvoje lice gledaju na Novo.

629
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, sve je tu.

630
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Postaneš Isusov prijatelj.

631
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se sve mijenju.

632
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer on je gospodar svega.

633
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato čuvajte se da vas razne praksa religijske i religijske i molitvene i ne znam kako da vas uništene.

634
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ih morate znati dobro upotrebiti.

635
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Molite, nije to što mi mislijo, to nije verbaliziranje nekih riječi.

636
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možete prvenstveno biti s njima prijatelj, slušati.

637
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] A onda mu reći diviti se, hvaliti ga.

638
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Duboko mu se pokloniti, reći genijalnosti.

639
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Podlubiti njegove rane na nogama i na rukama.

640
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je prava molita.

641
00:27:57,000 --> 00:28:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Iz trenutka u trenutak, dakle, da samo samo upijati ga.

642
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo Isus, raspolaži.

643
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imam povjerenja u tebe.

644
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost je dakle od tome da je Bog u tebi.

645
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo je Bog sveti.

646
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Niko sebe ne može napraviti sveti.

647
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako imitiraš svetost, to je najgore.

648
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vi sami znate kada na nogu.

649
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite pobožnu baku, joj, kak' je pobožna.

650
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ne znam razne druge, joj, pa ti se smrkne.

651
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to svetost.

652
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je pokušaj da imitiramo izvana ono što nema unutra.

653
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetost to je iznutra.

654
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je novi čovjek u tebi.

655
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je Bog u tebi.

656
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to razumijete, sve se razumije.

657
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ćete imati prismu da svako od nas može biti svet.

658
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] To uopće nije teško biti svet, prijatelji.

659
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svetac je čovjek koji mijenja društvo.

660
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji mijenja svijet.

661
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ako mislite što vi svojom molitvom da brbljate molitve.

662
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] U tome da vi postanete dobri mijenat krvatsko društvo.

663
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nećete.

664
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Začinit ćete ga stopu gori.

665
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako dopustite Bog da ovama bude.

666
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ćete vidjeti kako On preko vas i kroz vas stvara oko vas svjetlo.

667
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nove mogućnosti.

668
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nove međulutske odnose.

669
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako silovito mijenja.

670
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljude, društvo, politiku, kulturu.

671
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko ima uši neka čuje, kaže Isus.

672
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je gluh neka ide na otorino laringologa.

673
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je.

674
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad pitate dakle kako to i Nikola Tavilić i kardinat Stepinac.

675
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo to.

676
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa drugo ne čini čovjek.

677
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ostani ono što jesi.

678
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi seljak? Budi seljak dalje.

679
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi domačica? Budi.

680
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi učiteljica? Budi čovječe. Zavoli to.

681
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi muškarac? Budi.

682
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi naođenjeno? U želniću što prije.

683
00:29:58,000 --> 00:30:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje ga ti bio možeš postati svet. To nije problem.

684
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje ga ti bio.

685
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije teško prijateljiku raditi.

686
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Teško da se cijeli život muči da postane svet.

687
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što je Lutera uništilo? Zašto je odvojio se od katolička crkva?

688
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Od toga.

689
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je šao na ispovjed, mislio će ga ispovjed promijeta.

690
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao nutarnje muke.

691
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda nije bilo havioterapije.

692
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] A on je imao strašne nutarnje probleme.

693
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Grižne savjesti. Užasne stragove.

694
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on se mučio. Ispovjedu, ispovjedu.

695
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan. Ništa ni pomogu.

696
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je postio i postio. Ništa ni pomogu.

697
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je molio. Sve su govorili njegovi duhovnici nekrat.

698
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda došao u onu kulu gore.

699
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Visoku zatvorio se odnutra.

700
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad osnovnicu rimdanima čitao.

701
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] A moj će pravetnik živjeti od vjere.

702
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] I shvatio je. A vjera?

703
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je vjera? Povjerenje u jednu osnovu.

704
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam povjerenje u Isusa. Isu ti su prijatelj.

705
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] To ga je izbavilo.

706
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Al nažalost mi je bilo kasno tako da je išao razdijeliti crkvu.

707
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mesto da ih sastavio.

708
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] I da ih preobrazi.

709
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Umjesto da napravi reformu, napravi reformaciju.

710
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šteta.

711
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Razdijelili ste. Umjesto to.

712
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Umjesto da nastane nešto novo.

713
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali polako shvatio gdje moje rješenje.

714
00:31:25,000 --> 00:31:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome sledeći četvrtak svi da ste mi došli svijeti.

715
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjet ćete.

716
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta da napravite praktično.

717
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imajte vremena u danu.

718
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa se uzme najprije dvije minute.

719
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa se uzme pet minuta iza toga.

720
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa se uzme petnaest minuta.

721
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa pol sata.

722
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako imaš vremena?

723
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to na šetnji?

724
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi li u krevetu još nisi ustao pa imaš malo vremena pet minuta još.

725
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dok te sam ne uhvatim.

726
00:31:58,000 --> 00:32:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi li u crkvi.

727
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi li negdje doma sjediš u kuhnje bilo gdje.

728
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sijedi ili kleknji ili stoji.

729
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] I samo jedno.

730
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo se pospijesti.

731
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] To znači aktiviraj svoju duhovnu dimenziju.

732
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svoju osobnost.

733
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo shvati tu si ti bože.

734
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema i djete nema.

735
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu se ti si tu uskrsni moj Kristi.

736
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je tvoj duhov.

737
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] I poslije samo neko ulazi.

738
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ćete osjetiti.

739
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa posebno ne događa.

740
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ćete razočarani nekom pet šest minuta.

741
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ne znam dva dana čak.

742
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa posebno.

743
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znam kod ćete zapažati kako ljudi pažaju.

744
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti se promijenio.

745
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti kažeš kako?

746
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa ja zapažam.

747
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetac koji zapaža da je svet.

748
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije svetac.

749
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svetac je samo onaj gdje drugi.

750
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] to zapaze.

751
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] A on ne.

752
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kada on hoče zaparati on sa je ohol.

753
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] I misli da je nekako.

754
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] To nije to.

